<% content_for :titolo, "#{@pagina.titolo} - #{@pagina.numero}" %>

<div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-6 bg-white dark:bg-gray-900 text-black dark:text-white font-mono transition-colors duration-300"
     data-controller="exercise-checker page-viewer text-toggle font-controls"
     data-page-viewer-image-url-value="<%= asset_path('bus3_mat/p148/page.png') %>"
     data-text-toggle-target="content"
     data-font-controls-target="content">

  <!-- Header -->
  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Esercizio 1: Leggi e completa -->
  <div class="mb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks auto-advance">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
      <div class="flex items-center">
        <div class="bg-cyan-700 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0 z-10 relative">
          1
        </div>
        <span class="bg-yellow-300 text-cyan-700 font-bold pl-5 pr-4 py-1 rounded-r-full -ml-3">IMPARARE TUTTI</span>
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200"><strong>Leggi, osserva i disegni e completa.</strong></p>
    </div>

    <!-- Box spiegazione moltiplicazione -->
    <div class="bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 border-2 border-cyan-400 dark:border-cyan-500 rounded-lg p-4 mb-6">
      <p>La <strong class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">moltiplicazione</strong> permette di sommare più volte la stessa quantità.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-8">
      <!-- Problema A: Cioccolatini -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-cyan-300 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-4 items-center">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="bg-cyan-500 text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold inline-block mb-2">A</div>
            <p class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold mb-2">Domanda: Quanti cioccolatini ci sono nella scatola?</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <strong>Operazione →</strong>
                <span>4 +</span>
                <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="4"
                       class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center" inputmode="numeric">
                <span>+</span>
                <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="4"
                       class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center" inputmode="numeric">
                <span>=</span>
                <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="12"
                       class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center font-bold" inputmode="numeric">
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <strong class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">oppure →</strong>
                <span>4 ×</span>
                <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="3"
                       class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center" inputmode="numeric">
                <span>=</span>
                <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="12"
                       class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center font-bold" inputmode="numeric">
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 ml-8">↓</p>
              <p class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 ml-8">4 <span class="underline">ripetuto</span> volte</p>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mt-2"><strong>Risposta:</strong> Nella scatola ci sono
              <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="12"
                     class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center" inputmode="numeric">
              cioccolatini.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="dark:bg-white rounded-xl p-2 inline-block"><%= image_tag "bus3_mat/p148/output-1743504902148_664_358_280_175.png", alt: "Scatola di cioccolatini", class: "max-w-[200px] rounded-lg" %></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Problema B: Triangoli -->
      <div class="bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 border-2 border-cyan-300 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg p-4">
        <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-4 items-center">
          <div class="flex-1">
            <div class="bg-cyan-500 text-white px-2 py-0.5 rounded font-bold inline-block mb-2">B</div>
            <p class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 font-bold mb-2">Domanda: Quanti triangoli ci sono nel quadro?</p>
            <div class="space-y-2">
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <strong>Operazione →</strong>
                <span>6 +</span>
                <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="6"
                       class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center" inputmode="numeric">
                <span>+</span>
                <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="6"
                       class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center" inputmode="numeric">
                <span>=</span>
                <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="18"
                       class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center font-bold" inputmode="numeric">
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center gap-2 flex-wrap">
                <strong class="text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400">oppure →</strong>
                <span>6 ×</span>
                <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="3"
                       class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center" inputmode="numeric">
                <span>=</span>
                <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="18"
                       class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center font-bold" inputmode="numeric">
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200 mt-2"><strong>Risposta:</strong> Nel quadro ci sono
              <input type="text" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-correct-answer="18"
                     class="w-12 px-2 py-1 border-b-2 border-dotted border-gray-400 dark:border-gray-500 bg-transparent dark:text-white text-center" inputmode="numeric">
              triangoli.
            </p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex-shrink-0">
            <div class="dark:bg-white rounded-xl p-2 inline-block"><%= image_tag "bus3_mat/p148/output-1743504902148_654_574_294_185.png", alt: "Triangoli nel quadro", class: "max-w-[150px] rounded-lg" %></div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Esercizio 2: Risolvi i problemi -->
  <div class="mb-8">
    <div class="flex items-start gap-3 mb-4">
      <div class="bg-red-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center font-bold flex-shrink-0">
        2
      </div>
      <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">
        <strong>Risolvi i problemi sul quaderno.</strong>
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
      <div class="bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 border-2 border-cyan-300 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 mb-2">a.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">In una chitarra ci sono 6 corde. Quante corde ci sono in 8 chitarre?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 border-2 border-cyan-300 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 mb-2">b.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Alla fase finale di un torneo di pallavolo femminile sono state ammesse 10 squadre, ciascuna formata da 6 giocatrici. Quante giocatrici ci sono in tutto?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 border-2 border-cyan-300 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 mb-2">c.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Per una visita a un parco zoologico l'insegnante di una classe terza ha comprato 20 biglietti a € 8 l'uno. Qual è stata la spesa totale?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 border-2 border-cyan-300 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 mb-2">d.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Un impiegato lavora 8 ore al giorno. Quante ore lavora in 7 giorni?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 border-2 border-cyan-300 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 mb-2">e.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">In un teatro ci sono 54 file di poltrone. Ogni fila ha 10 poltrone. Quanti spettatori può accogliere il teatro?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 border-2 border-cyan-300 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg p-4">
        <p class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 mb-2">f.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">In una scatola ci sono 8 pennarelli. Quanti pennarelli ci sono in 9 scatole tutte uguali?</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-cyan-50 dark:bg-cyan-900/30 border-2 border-cyan-300 dark:border-cyan-600 rounded-lg p-4 md:col-span-2">
        <p class="font-bold text-cyan-600 dark:text-cyan-400 mb-2">g.</p>
        <p class="text-gray-700 dark:text-gray-200">Per andare all'allenamento di calcio Luigi percorre 6 chilometri al giorno. Quanti chilometri fa in una settimana?</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Footer con controlli -->
  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
